feed.title: GeoConnections CGDI Pilot Update Feed
feed.subtitle: This ATOM feed is used by provincial custodians to indicate the disposition of change proposals posted to the CGDI Pilot Feedback Feed. This feed can be monitored by clients to determine if their proposed change was accepted or rejected. Third parties, wishing to maintains a synchronized copy of all or part of the national Geobase, can use the contents of this feed to apply incrmental chages totheir Geobase copy.
